title: Fish & Streams
name: Fish & Streams
description: This shapefile contains the stream route reaches from the National Hydrography Dataset for all 4th-code subbasins that include any part of Montana.

properties.About: Our efforts focus on the restoration of in-stream flows, a multi-story riparian corridor (where conditions allow) and a full assemblage of native prairie fish.
properties.Data: Map shows the location of Box Elder and Telegraph Creeks, which have been the primary focus of our stream and fish activities.
